  "body": "<p>Hey there fangerines! It’s <a href=\"http://abstractinspiration.com/\">Zinia</a> here and today I’d like to share with you a really easy mixed media watercolor layout I created inspired from Amy’s latest collection Hustle &amp; Heart.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/4df167249dfcea43.jpg?v=1782797238\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>The whole idea started when I saw one of the cut apart cards from a paper called “The Little Things”.  I really loved the paint strokes on that card and the colors were arranged in a really beautiful order. So I decided to recreate that look on my background.</p><p>I took out my watercolor palettes and I tried to mix shades as close to that card as possible. Those colors go through the whole collection so using them for my background will ensure that all the embellishments will match perfectly with it.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/cf7086a388f93921.jpg?v=1782797241\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>So following the color order I painted some watercolor strokes with a flat wash application and a big flat brush.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/afa11abdae9eefd6.jpg?v=1782797244\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I let my watercolor background dry and meanwhile I cut a few floral images from other papers in the collection to use as embellishments.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/f3fc89466b0b1ca4.jpg?v=1782797247\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I wanted everything to be balanced and smooth so I decided to embellish my page by using color-coordinating products on top of each stripe. One of my favorite embellishments to use when I decorate my pages in a color coordinating style is clear stickers. Putting them on top of matching colors intensifies them and helps them pop.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/d29ea3cbfbcfe9b3.jpg?v=1782797249\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>As I was inspired from the card, I decided to use a white foam word for my title to create a similar look.</p><p>For a final touch, I decided to sprinkle some gold splatters using a Heidi Swapp color shine spray.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/141a7d91246b2191.jpg?v=1782797252\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Zinia<br/><a href=\"http://abstractinspiration.com/\">Abstract Inspiration Blog</a> | <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/abstractinspiration/\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"https://twitter.com/AbstractInsp\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AbstractInspirationPage\">Facebook</a></p><p><em>Thanks so much for sharing this layout with us, Zinia! Other Design Team member posts can be found </em><a href=\"http://www.amytangerine.com/blog/?category=amy+tangerine+design+team\"><em>here</em></a><em>. Shop HUSTLE &amp; HEART now on </em><em>our shop site</em><em>! </em></p><p><strong>SUPPLY LIST:</strong></p><p>341887 Hustle &amp; Heart - THICKERS The Lucky Ones | 341865 Hustle &amp; Heart - 12x12 Paper Coming Up Roses | 340873 Hustle &amp; Heart - 12x12 Paper Click Click | 340871 Hustle &amp; Heart - 12x12 Paper Floral Sensation | 341884 Hustle &amp; Heart - STICKER BOOK | 341892 Hustle &amp; Heart - 3D DIAMOND STICKERS | 341893 Hustle &amp; Heart - MINI FAUX SUEDE BOWS | 341889 Hustle &amp; Heart - PUFFY HEARTS | Heidi Swapp Gold Color Shine | Jane Davenport &amp; Prima Watercolors</p><p><em>Disclosure: Some of the links above are affiliate links. I receive a small percentage of sales at no cost to you. My creative partners and I really appreciate your continued support and every little bit helps me to bring you consistent content!</em></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
